item.title: CVE-2022-33202|2024-08-03T08:01:20.169Z -- softcreate%20corp. -- l2blocker
item.description: Authentication bypass vulnerability in the setup screen of L2Blocker(on-premise) Ver4.8.5 and earlier and L2Blocker(Cloud) Ver4.8.5 and earlier allows an adjacent attacker to perform an unauthorized login and obtain the stored information or cause a malfunction of the device by using alternative paths or channels for Sensor.
